data.description: This property offers 2100 square feet of peaceful & quiet living on 40 acres. Two parcels, house on 5 acres, plus 35 acres of land under one tax lot. The home offers spacious living room with full wall of windows facing East. Open double entry leads to striking white and black decor kitchen with center island with cabinet & drawers. Kitchen is open to connecting oversized eating area or family room., with several windows to front of property. Enter the office/all purpose room from the hallway, that also leads to the primary bedroom with oversized walk-in closet. Split beds opposite end of home, as is the main bath. Circle driveway leads to house and the attractive 20' X 10' storage shed wood floor & small loft. Several outbuildings 24' X 24' shop with cement floor, 220 electric, 50 amp for RV hookup. Pump house and 3 other smaller sheds for storage. Please excuse all the boxes invarious rooms sellers area packing for the move. Easy to show, so call your buyers.,
